description: The video is a security camera shot. The video starts with a shot of a light grey wall and a wooden post, with a concrete floor and a shadowy figure on the floor in the distance.  There is a security camera and a mailbox on the right side of the frame, as well as a piece of black metal on the left.  The camera then pans down to show the black metal object more clearly; it is a folding chair. The camera is pointed directly at the middle of the doorway and it captures the sound of a car driving by.  The shadow of a car is also visible on the wall as well as the shadow of the wooden post on the floor.  The sound of the car driving by fades and the video ends.

This video is a still shot of a door with a fisheye lens. It is taken from inside the doorway. There is a large black and white picture hanging to the right, and a door to another room is slightly visible to the left. The camera is facing the front door. It is locked with the handle and deadbolt locked. The video begins with the date and time displayed in the upper left corner. The door is closed and still throughout the video.

The video is a security camera footage of the front porch of a house. There is a wicker chair to the left, and a stone slab on the front steps. A piece of furniture or clothing lies on the floor, possibly a throw rug, at the edge of the frame. The camera is facing the front door, which is slightly open. Outside the porch is a concrete sidewalk and a patch of green grass. It is daytime and the sun is shining. There is no movement in the video except for leaves rustling in the wind.  The audio is a quiet wind noise with a high-pitched squeak in the background.

The video is a still shot of a street corner in a suburban neighborhood. There is a white car parked at the corner. In the background there is a house with a brown roof and a blue siding. The house has a large tree in front of it,  and a driveway that leads to the house. There is a red car parked in the driveway. There are large trees lining the street on either side of the house. The sky is blue with some clouds in the distance. The video is recorded from a home surveillance camera, as the video frame is slightly distorted. The video has a date and time stamp in the top left corner: 2024-05-28 14:58:02.

This is a black-and-white security camera video of a backyard at night.  The video begins with a person wearing a dark hooded jacket standing in the middle of the yard, their back turned to the camera.  In the foreground, a small shed is visible with a wooden deck attached to the back.  There are some chairs on the deck and two objects laying on the ground in front of it.  To the left, a black car is partially visible in the driveway.  In the background, there is a single-wide mobile home and a basketball hoop, while a large SUV is parked in the driveway, facing the camera.  A street lamp is positioned between the black car and the mobile home, which is casting a glow on the area.  The person in the middle of the yard seems to be looking around, possibly checking to see if anyone is around before approaching the shed.  The video is silent.

The video is from a security camera and shows a yellow car parked in the driveway of a house. The date and time are displayed in the top left corner of the screen. The camera is positioned looking out from a covered porch, and there is a small plant to the left of the camera. The camera is facing a street with houses on both sides. The video is 45 seconds long and does not show anyone or anything moving.

The video shows a street with a security camera in the upper right corner. It is dark outside and a single street lamp is illuminating the street in front of the camera. There are some power lines in front of the camera and a palm tree to the right. A faint noise can be heard, but it is difficult to make out. The date and time of the video is shown in the upper left corner, 2021-05-28 02:08:24. The video continues for 25 seconds.

The video is a black and white recording from a security camera. It shows a woman sitting on the edge of a bed, facing the camera. She is wearing a white long-sleeved shirt, black pajamas, and white socks with cartoon characters on them. She is looking at a smartphone and using her left hand to operate the screen. There is another bed to the left, with a blanket on it and a remote control on a small table beside it. There is also a nightstand to the right of the main bed, with an object on it, which is out of focus. The woman is hunched over the phone, and the screen is lit up, casting a bright glow on her face.  There is a slight humming noise in the background.

The video is a black and white night time security camera recording of a backyard.  There is a small tree in the center of the yard, and a planter in the upper right corner.  A string of lights stretches across the yard horizontally.  A large, dark, unidentified object appears to move in the lower left corner of the yard.  At about 0:24, the object appears to be making a noise similar to a "peep".

The video shows the interior of a store with a silver car parked outside. There is a bench in the store and a shelf with shoes on it. The car is parked just outside a glass double-door. A woman walks into the store, looking at her cell phone. She is wearing black sneakers, blue jeans and a blue t-shirt. As she walks by, the microphone picks up the sound of an electric car charging and the sound of a car door opening and closing.

The video is a still shot of a living room, the camera is pointing toward a hallway leading to the kitchen. The living room is cluttered with furniture, including a grey couch, two chairs, a coffee table with a glass top, and a TV console with a flat screen TV. The kitchen is visible in the background, with two people standing at the kitchen counter. In the hallway, a young boy is standing in front of the kitchen door, holding a piece of paper in his hand. He is reading from the paper, and talking. The audio is muffled but the speaker sounds like a woman, and she's talking to the boy.

The video shows a security camera recording of the outside of a building. A white door with a white security gate is in the center of the frame. There is a window with a white security gate to the left.  There is a green mop leaning against the door. A crack runs across the wall and ceiling. You can hear an audible "p" sound towards the end of the clip.

The video is a black and white night-vision recording of a baby's room. The camera is pointing towards the crib, which is empty. The date and time are displayed in the upper left corner of the screen. A fan is running in the background, making a consistent whooshing noise. The sound of a baby crying is heard sporadically. The video ends before the baby is brought back into the room.

The video shows a security camera view of a gate opening, revealing a grassy area.  The camera is mounted near a yucca plant, and the date and time are displayed in the upper left corner of the screen.  There is a loud, high-pitched, repeating sound throughout the clip.

The video is a night-time security camera recording. The camera is angled slightly upward, looking out over a yard with trees and a driveway in the background. The camera's night vision is on and the image is in black and white.  There are a few blurry patches of light from streetlights in the distance. The camera catches a car driving past and there is a single strong beam of light, possibly from a vehicle's headlights, flashing on and off for a few seconds. It's difficult to discern any other activity in the video but it's likely a typical recording from a security camera.

The video is a black and white, grainy view of what appears to be the inside of a piece of machinery or equipment.  The camera is angled so that it appears to be looking up.  Three metal pieces come together at the top center of the frame, with the camera focused on the small space in between them. The metal pieces extend to the edges of the frame, with a small sliver of white space to the bottom and right.  The video is static and the only movement comes from the graininess of the camera.  This video likely comes from a security camera or a device that is monitoring the functioning of the machine.

The video shows a brick wall with a black and white tiled floor in the bottom right corner. The video is taken from a low angle and points upwards towards the wall. There appears to be a blue brush in the top right corner of the video, but it’s hard to tell because it is so far away. The video has a timestamp that reads "2024-05-20 02:31:59" and starts ticking upwards as the video progresses. At the 25-second mark, a very faint "peeping" sound can be heard, but it is unclear what is making the sound.  The video is very still and the only movement is the timestamp ticking upward.

The video shows a black and white image of what appears to be a fish swimming in dark, murky water. The camera is positioned to look down at the fish from above, as it swims toward the right edge of the frame. The time and date are displayed on the screen in the top left corner. The video does not contain audio, and there is no context or information about the fish or the filming location.

The video shows a security camera view of an apartment complex courtyard. The camera is positioned at a slight downward angle, looking out from a hallway. There is a green lawn in the courtyard, surrounded by shrubs. A large tree is leaning to the right and casting shadows on the lawn. A black bird can be seen in the video, perched on the edge of the hallway to the left of the frame. It then flies away from the frame.  The video is only 35 seconds long and there is no audio.

The video is a still shot from a security camera. It shows a dimly lit dining room with a large window opening to the kitchen. There is a chandelier hanging from the ceiling.  A chair with a pink blanket draped over it is visible in the foreground.  A rolling cart with a plaid blanket draped over it is visible on the right side of the window. The timestamp on the video indicates it is from May 27th 2024.
Exception occurred

The video shows a backyard patio with a large, gray deck. The camera is pointed down at the deck from a high angle, and there are several pieces of furniture visible, including a table and chairs, a coffee table, and two couches. There is also a large, black grill in the background, and a patio heater on the left side of the frame. There is some greenery to the right of the patio and a small plastic play structure to the left. A figure is visible in the background, walking in front of the patio railings.

The video starts with a woman walking into the kitchen. She is carrying a white container in her right hand. As she walks she is talking on her phone.  She walks over to the counter and puts the container down. She begins to pull items out of the container, looking for something. The camera is positioned in the dining room, which is located to the right of the kitchen. There are two green upholstered chairs to the right of the table. The woman's face is not visible because the camera is in the dining room, the woman's back is to the camera. After looking for something in the container for a few seconds she pulls out a plastic bottle and pours something into a cup on the counter. The woman then puts the container back on the counter. She then goes to reach into a cabinet to grab something.  The video ends with the woman rummaging around in the cabinet.

The video is a black and white night vision security camera footage. The camera is facing the exterior of a building and is pointed at a plant that is in the grass in front of the building. The plant is tall and has large leaves. The camera is mounted on a wall and is surrounded by brick and stucco. The only other object visible in the video is a shadow from the side of the building. A timestamp in the top left corner of the screen indicates the video was taken on 05/27/2024 at 23:31:09. It is night-time and the camera captures some movement of the plant, potentially from the wind. Just before the video ends at 23:31:44, a distinct noise of a bird screeching can be heard.

The video is from a doorbell camera and is black and white. It's nighttime, the time is 9:18 PM. The video is focused on the front of a house, you can see a driveway, a yard, and a bush. There is a house in the distance, but it is not clear. There are lights in the distance, and you can hear a car driving past.

The video is a security camera recording from a hallway in a home. The camera is mounted on the wall, looking down the hallway. There are two open doorways visible, one on the left and one on the right. The hallway walls are painted white and the ceiling has a single lightbulb. The "Life is Good" sign is centered on the wall opposite the camera. A young man walks into view at the right doorway carrying a small, white box. He walks towards the left doorway, glancing to his left as he does. He disappears from view, then reappears after a few seconds.  He continues to walk left, looking at the box he is carrying, then exits the left doorway.  The man's face is not visible.  The video has no audio.

The video is taken from a doorbell camera. It shows a black SUV parked on a gravel driveway. The date and time, "2024-05-28 07:09:18" is displayed in the top left corner. The front of the vehicle is facing the camera. The license plate, "BGZ-830," is visible. The driveway is surrounded by a green lawn and a few bushes. The video appears to be a recording of the doorbell camera's activity. The sound is of a bird chirping.  The person who recorded the video was likely trying to capture any activity near the door, but it does not show any people approaching or leaving.

The video shows a security camera footage from the inside of a store. The camera is pointing towards the door. A woman in a dark green shirt and dark shorts is seen entering the store. She is pushing a shopping cart, and it appears she is struggling to maneuver it through the doorway. She is trying to get the cart through a narrow door with a security gate.  She pushes and pulls the cart, trying to make it fit. She repeats this several times, but the cart gets stuck in the doorway. The video ends with her pushing the cart into the store.

The video shows a metal bending machine in a workshop. There are stacks of metal rods and some other metal pieces on the floor. A man’s voice can be heard speaking in Spanish, but the audio is very muffled, and it’s impossible to understand what is being said. It is unclear what is happening in the video or what the man is doing.

The video shows three candles burning in a room. The candles are all different sizes and colors. The candle on the left is green, the middle candle is white, and the candle on the right is orange. The middle candle is in a clear glass and has handwriting on it.  At the top of the handwriting it appears to say "28/May" and underneath that it says "10:25 AM."  The camera appears to be stationary and filming the candles from a distance. The video is only 25 seconds long.

The video shows a white wall with a few small holes in it. It appears to be a security camera footage captured on May 28, 2024 at 07:44:55. The camera angle is a bit off center and tilted upwards towards the top of the wall. A shadow of a tree or a bush can be seen moving across the wall due to the sunlight passing through the leaves.

The video is from a security camera.  It shows a blue SUV parked in a gravel driveway.  A white camper trailer is parked to the left of the driveway, and there is a wooden shed to the right of the driveway.  Trees are in the background.   The date and time of the video is displayed in the top left corner: 2024-05-28 18:34:31.  There is no activity other than birds chirping in the background.

The video shows a close-up view of a blue metal garage door. The door is slightly open, and there is a small gap between the two sections of the door. The door is made of metal panels, and there is a metal frame around the edge. The top of the door is partially visible, and there is a white concrete wall above the door. The door is making a rattling sound as it is opening.

The video shows a scene from a security camera pointed out of a window. The camera is pointing towards a grassy courtyard with a few trees in the front and an apartment building in the back. The camera shows a woman pushing a stroller through the courtyard. The woman is wearing a light pink shirt. The camera is showing a live view and the date and time are shown in the upper left corner of the video.

The video starts with a view of a green lawn with a few trees in the background. The camera is mounted on the side of a building, looking out over the lawn. In the foreground, we can see a truck with a black and white table in the bed. The timestamp on the video indicates that it was recorded on May 28, 2024, at 11:00:34 am. A few seconds later, the camera pans left to show a close-up of the side of the building, with some leaves on the ground. There is a lot of wind blowing in the video, and the trees are swaying back and forth. The wind makes a whistling sound that can be heard in the video.  The camera remains focused on the side of the building throughout the video.

The video is a black and white night-time recording from a trail camera, looking out over a patch of grass. There is some dense foliage on the left-hand side of the frame. At the start, the camera is picking up a faint, high-pitched humming sound. This sound continues for about 3 seconds, then fades. It starts again at 0:09 and continues for another 3 seconds, then fades away again. At 0:10, the camera captures a very brief flash of light at the edge of the grass. No further sounds or visual activity are picked up until 0:21, when a high-pitched chirping sound becomes audible.

The video shows a black and white, night-time view of a street, captured on a security camera. The camera is positioned on a building overlooking the street. Two bright streetlights illuminate the street. There are multiple houses lining the street, some with fences, and a few utility poles. The street is paved with gravel and has a few weeds growing on the sides. A few power lines hang from the utility poles across the top of the frame. In the distance, a vehicle's headlights appear and disappear as the car drives down the street. The time and date appear on the screen, showing the video was captured on May 28, 2021 at 03:59:27. A sound of birds chirping can be heard in the background. At 00:28, a car's horn honks loudly.
The video is a black and white night time recording from a security camera. The camera is pointing up towards the ceiling of a parking garage, showing the underside of parked cars.

The video is black and white and shows a living room and kitchen. The audio is unclear and muffled, but it appears to be a conversation between three people: a man, a woman, and a child. The man is sitting in a black recliner in the living room, looking down at something on his lap. The woman is sitting on the couch with a child, and it seems like the woman is reading. The video cuts to the kitchen, which is messy and cluttered. The sink is full of dirty dishes, and the countertops are covered in various items, including a leafy green vegetable. The camera then cuts back to the living room, where the man is still looking at something on his lap. The audio is still unclear, but the man and woman seem to be discussing something. The child is playing on the floor in front of the couch. The video is shot with a security camera and is likely from a home. It gives the viewer a glimpse into the everyday lives of a family.

The video is taken from a security camera in a living room. It shows a woman in a blue and yellow dress walking towards a closed door on the right side of the frame. She opens the door and goes outside.  There is a couch, piano, and coffee table in the room. The camera is mounted on the coffee table.

The video starts with a view from the top of a staircase looking down into a living room. There is a man sitting on a floral couch in the foreground. There is a white, fluffy carpet that covers the floor. The living room has tall, arched windows with teal drapes, and a large, crystal chandelier hanging from the ceiling. There are two couches facing each other, and a coffee table between them. There is a fireplace on the right side of the room, and a plant in the corner. The camera pans over to the left, towards the windows. The man on the couch is no longer visible. The video ends with a close-up of the plant and the windows. The sounds in the video are mostly ambient noise, including muffled voices and the sound of water running. There is also a loud, whooshing sound at the end of the video.

The video is a blurry recording from a security camera. It begins with a close-up of a white, translucent curtain. The curtain is slightly waving in the wind, revealing a blurry view of green grass and foliage.  As the camera pans out, the view becomes increasingly blurry and obscured by the waving curtain. Eventually, the camera shows a light grey cloudy sky. This indicates that the security camera is likely placed in an outdoor area, possibly facing a yard or other outdoor space. The video is of poor quality with a grainy texture and blur, making it difficult to discern details. The camera’s low resolution and shaky footage suggests that it could be an older model or that it is malfunctioning. Overall, this video is a brief, blurry recording from a security camera, providing a limited view of a possible outdoor environment.

The video is a close up shot of a woman's arm, from the elbow to her chest.  She has long blonde hair, is wearing a white shirt and a black scrunchie on her wrist.  White earphones are in her ears and she is looking down at her hands, which are out of frame.  The woman is speaking in Portuguese but it's difficult to understand what she is saying.  The audio cuts off after the woman says "não tem problema hoje se você sentar na cadeira de qualquer forma".  The words "2021-05-20 06:38:34" appear in the top left corner of the screen.

The video is a recording from a security camera. The camera is facing a living room. There is a couch, a TV, a refrigerator, a table, a chair and a doorway leading to a bathroom. On the TV, a movie is playing with a close up of a man's face. A person is sitting on the floor next to the sink in the bathroom. The audio is of two people talking, but it is unclear what they are saying.

The video is from a security camera. The camera is pointed at a gate leading to a backyard. The date and time are shown in the top left corner of the video, which is May 28th, 2024 at 6:47:26 AM. A truck is parked in the driveway, facing the camera. The truck's bed is empty and appears to be made of wood. The truck bed is covered with a tarp, and there is a metal rod across the top of the bed. A basket is sitting on the ground to the left of the truck. The gate is made of metal bars, with several other metal bars extending from the ground to the top. A sound of someone honking a horn can be heard shortly after the video starts. The person is trying to get someone's attention. They honk a second time, which is also the sound at the end of the video. The camera's field of view is narrow, and the quality of the video is somewhat grainy. The video cuts off before we can see who is in the truck or why they are there.

The video is a security camera shot in a kitchen. The camera is mounted high on the wall in a corner and provides a wide view of the room. The shot begins with a young Black woman wearing an orange tank top standing at the kitchen counter in front of a stainless steel refrigerator. She is facing away from the camera and is preparing food in a glass bowl. She is stirring the food with a wooden spoon. In the background, the kitchen island is piled high with grocery bags and boxes. The dining room is behind the island, and a television set can be seen on the wall. The woman continues stirring her food and then walks out of the camera's view. The date and time are displayed in the upper left-hand corner of the screen. The video ends with the sound of the woman taking several loud bites out of something she's eating.

The video shows a black and white night-vision view of a driveway. There are trees on the left side of the frame and a wooden post on the right side of the frame. In the distance, you can see a white van parked in the driveway. The date and time are shown on the top left corner of the screen: 2024-05-28 04:47:39. There are a few small, undefined objects in the background that could possibly be a trash can, a chair, or a pile of leaves. The camera is angled slightly down and the viewer can see a bit of the grass and a plastic tarp on the ground to the right of the frame.  The only sound in the video is a quick "beep" at the 0:28 mark.

The video shows a black and white night time view of a backyard with a hammock hanging between two poles. The hammock is empty. There is a bench on the right side of the frame, next to a wooden fence. There is a trash can on the left side of the frame, behind the fence. The camera is looking out from under a roof that is made of wooden beams. The timestamp on the video is May 27th, 2024, at 11:56 PM. There is a light on in the distance that illuminates the road outside the fence. There is movement in the distance, possibly a car driving by.

The video is taken from a security camera and shows a road with a white line and two yellow lines running down the middle. There are some power lines running across the top of the video. The camera is situated facing the road and appears to be mounted above the road on the right side of the road. Some trees can be seen in the background. A blue car, a red motorcycle, and a white pickup truck all drive down the road in the video. The date and time appear in the top left corner of the video.

This is a black and white video from a security camera. It is a wide-angle lens. The date and time are in the top left corner of the screen: 05/27/2024 20:46:45. A man in a white tank top is standing in the doorway, fiddling with something. The door is white. There is a piece of art on the wall to the right of the door and another open doorway on the left.

This is a black and white video from a security camera. It shows the outside of a house at night. A tree is in the foreground and there is a brick driveway leading up to a gate. In the distance, there is a street and a white car with its headlights on is visible.  A person wearing dark clothing walks past the driveway toward the white car and out of the camera's range.  It is a quiet night and the only sounds are the rustling of leaves and some distant animal sounds.  The video ends with a loud bang that sounds like an explosion.

This is a night time security camera video of a person walking toward the camera and then turning to walk away. The camera is placed on a porch with a white car in the background to the left. A set of steps lead to a small landing and then a walkway leading off to the right. There are boxes and a plant on the landing to the right. The person is wearing a dark shirt and shorts. They appear to be carrying something, but it is difficult to see what it is.  The person is walking towards the camera, and then turns and walks away,  as if they were walking around the porch.  When the person walks away,  the sound of a small dog barking can be heard, and then a beep sound.

The video is a black and white, grainy, static shot of a dark space with a light gray area in the upper right corner. There is a small, faint, dark shape near the top center of the screen that doesn't move. The date 05/28/2024 and the time 00:03:12 are displayed in the top left corner. The word "kami" is in the bottom left corner. It seems to be a security camera feed from a night-time scene.

The video shows a front porch of a house with a door and a welcome mat. The door is slightly ajar and a black curtain is blowing in the breeze. A car is parked in the driveway to the right.  A blue recycling bin is visible to the right of the porch.  The date and time, "05/28/2024 15:05:07", are displayed at the top left corner. Just before the audio cuts out, a "peeping" sound is heard, similar to a bird.

The video is a black and white night vision recording from a security camera.  It shows a dark room with a closed white door in the center of the frame. There is a dark brown dresser to the left with various items on top of it, including a television.  A thin vertical line is visible in the lower left corner of the frame.  It seems like a person is outside the door, slowly moving back and forth.  The video ends before the person's appearance is clear.  The date and time are visible on the screen, it is 5/28/2024 14:28:36. There is a soft sound of a person breathing and possibly saying a few words, but the sound is very unclear.

The video shows a still image of a security camera overlooking a field. There are parallel rows in the field that appear to be some type of crops. A red-painted roof with some sort of metal structure sits in the foreground. There is a concrete curb separating the field from a paved road. In the background, there is a building. In the bottom left corner, there are some barbed wire fence posts and what appears to be a blue plastic bottle. The date and time, "2024-05-28 13:09:26", is displayed in the top left corner of the video. After approximately 23 seconds, a loud "peep" sound plays, and the video ends.

The video shows a security camera's view of a brick wall and a bush. The camera is looking up at the wall and bush at a steep angle. The time stamp on the video shows that it is May 28, 2024 at 09:58:39.  A small brown bird appears in the lower right side of the video at 0:20 and then makes a bird sound at 0:21. It is unclear what kind of bird it is, but it appears to be a sparrow or similar.

The video is a still shot of a grassy field with two buildings on the property. A small white garage with two large garage doors is in the foreground, and behind it is a larger, white, industrial building with two large doors. A dirt path runs between the two buildings, with a short concrete path leading to the garage. The grass on the field is green, and there is a line of trees in the distance. The sky is bright blue and a few white clouds are visible. The video is likely from a security camera, as there is a timestamp in the upper left corner of the screen. It is a still shot and there is no movement in the video. The camera’s focus is slightly off and the image is slightly blurry.
The video shows a woman talking on her phone. She's in a living room with a dog and appears to be trying to get her dog to leave the room by opening a door. The dog seems to be reluctant to leave.

The video is taken from a security camera mounted on a house. The camera is pointed towards the driveway. The video starts with a black SUV parked in the driveway, the camera is facing the roof of the vehicle. A white SUV can be seen parked on the street. A person gets out of the driver's seat of the black SUV, goes around the vehicle and gets in the driver's seat of the white SUV. The person then drives off in the white SUV.

The video shows three candles. The first candle is a small green candle in a cylindrical glass container. The second candle is a white candle in a glass jar with writing on the side. The third candle is an orange candle in a cylindrical orange container. The orange candle and the white candle are both lit. There is a metal bucket and a large round object visible in the background. The camera is still and stationary.  There is a sound of something being blown on a microphone at the end of the video.

The video shows a black and white image of a door opening. The camera is placed at a low angle, pointing upwards towards the door, which is open at an angle. The door is mostly dark, with a thin, white line visible along the top edge. The sound of the door opening can be heard in the background, making a quiet and continuous “p” sound.

The video is a security camera footage of a small grocery store. The camera is mounted on the ceiling and looking down on the counter area. The counter is made of wood and has a cash register, a scale, and a few other items on it. There are shelves full of goods behind the counter. A sign that reads "Coca-Cola" is visible on the wall. The video is silent and does not show any people.

The video is shot from a security camera outside a home. It is a cloudy day, and the ground is wet from rain.  Three dogs are standing in the driveway, eating from a bowl. One of the dogs is in the background, partially obscured by a barrel. There is a man in a red shirt and black pants standing in the driveway, holding a container. He reaches toward a barrel to his left, and pours something into a bowl on the ground. As he does so, he is looking at the dogs in the distance. When the pouring is finished, he turns his head and begins to walk away.  The dogs continue to eat from the bowls on the ground. A fence and gate are visible in the background.  The dogs are all brown and white, and seem to be a mix of Saint Bernard and Akita. The man is about 40 years old, of average height and build.  The sound of the man pouring from the container is audible. He also makes a sound like, "p-p-p"  as he walks away.

The video shows a security camera view of a garage, with the camera facing a garage door. The garage door is open, and a man walks in.
